1. group_expert_vs_control_cii.m

Purpose

This script performs the basic group-level comparison between expert meditators and controls.

It computes:

Baseline CII
Meditation CII
Group means
Paired t-tests
Group comparison boxplot
What It Does
For each subject:
Baseline CII

Computed using: EO1↔EC1,EO1↔G1,EC1↔G1

Meditation CII

Computed using: M1↔(EO1,EC1,G1) and M2↔(EO2,EC2,G2)

Output
Numerical Results
Expert baseline mean
Expert meditation mean
Control baseline mean
Control meditation mean
p-values

Plot
Expert vs Control comparison boxplot


2. group_expert_control_full_analysis_FINAL.m

It includes:

Full statistical testing
